    <item>
      <title>Fastest Way to Create Money Making Videos</title>
      <link>http://www.videoboss2011.com/61/create-money-making-videos/</link>
      <comments>http://www.videoboss2011.com/61/create-money-making-videos/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jun 2011 19:24:45 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Video Boss</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Video Boss]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.videoboss2011.com/?p=61</guid>
      <description>There are several ways to make money online, be it selling info products or selling physical products or selling services or even promoting affiliate offers, the fastest way to do it is by creating video.  And you could create such money making videos in 5 simple steps Step-1: Writing the video script Don’t be scared [...]&lt;p&gt;A post from: &lt;a href="http://www.videoboss2011.com"&gt;Video Boss Bonus | Video Boss Review&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/video-boss-bonus-video-boss-review/Video_Boss_Bonus_-_Video_Boss_Review-Fastest_Way_to_Create_Money_Making_Videos.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There are several ways to make money online, be it selling info products or selling physical products or selling services or even promoting affiliate offers, the fastest way to do it is by creating video.  And you could create such money making videos in 5 simple steps</p>
<p><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Step-1: Writing the video script</span></em></p>
<p>Don’t be scared by the word video scripting, it simply means what you are going to say in the video. And you can easily create video that keeps the visitor glued to your video by using this simple FAB video scripting technique</p>
<p>FEATURES, ADVANTAGES and BENEFITS – yes this is the FAB technique</p>
<p>Let’s say you want to promote a video camera on Amazon. Head over to the product page on Amazon, for example the Kodak zi8 pocket video camera page. Now you will see that Amazon has a list of product features and that means half the work is already done.</p>
<p>Here is one of the features of the Kodak zi8 pocket video camera page “take full HD 1080p videos wherever you go”.</p>
<p>So what is the advantage of this feature? Full 1080p is the highest resolution of high definition video available and that means you can create videos of very high quality with this camera.</p>
<p>So what are the benefits of this feature? You could capture your child’s cheerful smile, those funny moments you will cherish forever and more. Here is where the magic happens. People look for benefits rather the features. Feature is a quantitative way of describing the product. However benefits are the emotional experience from using the product.</p>
<p>And this simple FAB video scripting template is the basis of successful sales videos, infomercials and direct response marketing videos. So take each feature and apply the FAB video scripting layout and you will have long enough script to craft a 3-5 minute sales video or even longer. Follow this simple formula and you will have created a killer video script. Once you create the video script the next thing is</p>
<p><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Step-2: Video Opener</span></em></p>
<p>Well this is not some weirdo beer opener. Video opener is basically what you say in the very first screen on your video. You have got 8-15 seconds to grab the viewers’ attention and get them to watch the full video. So your video intros that make up the first 8-15 seconds is the critical element that decides whether your video is going to be a winner or dud.</p>
<p>Try this 3 part video opener</p>
<p>Part-1:  [In this video I am going to show you why]</p>
<p>Part-2:  [The Kodak zi8 is going to revolutionize the way you make your personal videos]</p>
<p>Part-3:  [And why it might be the only camera you'll ever need - saving you money and making it simple for you to create video]</p>
<p>First you tell them there is a reason WHY they should WATCH this video. Next you tell them the KEY OUTCOME they will get by following your advice. And finally you tell how the video will HELP them save time and money.</p>
<p>It’s so simple! Now you take this 3-part opener and use it with any product that you promote, just make part 2 and part 3 appropriate for the product that you are promoting.  And this simple formula serves as the perfect video intros for YouTube videos.</p>
<p>Well we have covered a lot of ground so far, go ahead apply this and I will be back with the next 3 steps of producing your killer sales video like a video boss.</p>
<p>A post from: <a href="http://www.videoboss2011.com">Video Boss Bonus | Video Boss Review</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
